OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fthickening to bring occasional rain,
OL,7,Fthis focused across western areas of
OL,8,FCentral and Tayside, with little
OL,9,Fexpected to penetrate to the coast.
OL,10,FSoutherly coastal winds initially
OL,11,Ffresh.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FCoastal districts milder
OL,14,Fthan Tuesday. Elsewhere significantly
OL,15,Fcooler. Rather cloudy morning with a
OL,16,Flittle light rain, mostly confined
OL,17,Facross far west. Mainly dry for the
OL,18,Fafternoon with brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
